Jess Barker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jess_Barker 0 Jess Barker (June 4, 1912 – August 8, 2000) was an American film actor of the 1930s and 1940s. He is probably most famous for being the first husband of actress Susan Hayward. Jess_Barker ( June_4_,_1912 – August_8_,_2000 ) was an_American_film_actor of the_1930s_and_1940s .
